                <h1>Diego Maradona: The Legend of Football</h1>
                <p>Diego Maradona, an iconic Argentinian football player, is hailed as one of the greatest in history. His extraordinary skills, vision, and dribbling set him apart. Maradona's career peaked in the 1986 World Cup, where he led Argentina to victory with unforgettable moments, including the "Hand of God" goal and the legendary solo run against England.</p>
